      {
        "id": 4281902,
        "name": "J\u00fcrgen Schmidt",
        "username": "Martin_Zwick",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/m/9fc29f/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2024-01-30T11:40:04.364Z",
        "cooked": "<p><strong>2020 Domaine Jean-Claude Bachelet et Fils Puligny-Montrachet \u201eLes Aubues\u201c</strong></p>\n<p>What a relief this Puligny-Montrachet was after a disppointing and \u201e<em>one-dimensiona</em>l\u201c 2017 Huber Chardonnay AR Magnum. Here it is all about finesse&amp;elegance and noblesse. In case of Huber it was all about a wannabe Puligny-Montrachet. Yes, I am a bit harsh/mean. <img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/images/emoji/unicode/face_with_hand_over_mouth.png?v=12\" title=\":face_with_hand_over_mouth:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":face_with_hand_over_mouth:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>The PM is soo delicious, you would want to drown in it.  Flowers, juicy fruit, spice, brioche and a chalky finish.  Mmmmmh\u2026\u2026\u2026</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/original/4X/6/a/e/6aea13321ae76dde2c2cfd227125a3a432dc269d.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/6aea13321ae76dde2c2cfd227125a3a432dc269d\" title=\"IMG_9621\"><img src=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/4X/6/a/e/6aea13321ae76dde2c2cfd227125a3a432dc269d_2_294x500.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_9621\" data-base62-sha1=\"ffO78QUqcr7Mz2ZlxreSQePVTNX\" width=\"294\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/4X/6/a/e/6aea13321ae76dde2c2cfd227125a3a432dc269d_2_294x500.jpeg, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/4X/6/a/e/6aea13321ae76dde2c2cfd227125a3a432dc269d_2_441x750.jpeg 1.5x, https://www.wineberserkers.com/uploads/db0731/optimized/4X/6/a/e/6aea13321ae76dde2c2cfd227125a3a432dc269d_2_588x1000.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"7B6C51\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_9621</span><span class=\"informations\">2376\u00d74030 1.62 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
