        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/e47774/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2024-01-30T13:20:08.209Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Nice stuff guys! On Puligny, we opened a 2017 J.M. Boillot Champs-Canet (1er cru) this weekend that really blew our socks off. It was fairly old school and could definitely go longer, but was not big and blowsy\u2013just big, fruited, framed well with integrating oak. It had a crystalline quality and balance and an outstanding finish.</p>",
